data.description: Conveniently located culdesac street with very little traffic, walking distance to West Navarre Primary School and access to the best amenities in all of Navarre! *2020 Roof & water heater, new oven/microwave combo, garage door opener, fence, light fixtures, ceiling fans, and New LVP flooring.  This 4 bedroom, 3 bath, full brick home has an open floor plan with a screened porch. Plenty of space for entertaining indoors & a huge backyard with shade trees for outdoor living to include a fire pit. Holley By The Sea offers 48 acre recreations center to include - clay tennis courts, golf, Beach house for events, Lap pool, Baby pool, Family pool, Full weight room & cardio, Volleyball court, pickleball, Ball field, Basketball court, Youth department for before & after school care and summer camp.
